title: Compensation for victims of property loss due to market price stabilization !
body:
Compensation for victims of property loss due to market price stabilization ! 

Claims to victims of divided assets in half due to pancakes stabilizing their prices relative to the market

I bought TXL on a pancake for 1.1 but the price was reduced by 50% because the pancake equalized the price against coinmarketcap.
I am one of those victims, please join me in supporting the compensation for the victims
author: 0xF5a9ee2Ba013adFc5Bf7412eb186a32d9677ba03
